race.description: Bold Construction Group F&M Mdn Hcp
race.comment: The well-related HIGHGROVE ROSE (5) (half to G2 winner Not An Option) resumes here but got up to Listed level when last in work and has tuned up for this with a recent trial placing. Can run a race while fresh. HIGHLAND KITTY (2) just missed the placings in both career outings before being tipped out for further time to furnish. Has top-three credentials. BELLOVE (10) strips fitter third-up from the spell and only needs some luck navigating from the sticky draw to be playing a role in the finish. BROWN RIVER (1) is facing the starter for the first time and any market confidence must be noted. Include.
